snippet.title: Travis Scott Furiously Reacts To Facing $750 Million Astroworld Lawsuit
snippet.description:
Travis Scott Furiously Reacts To Facing $750 Million Astroworld Lawsuit 
Travis Scott’s fan base often refer to him as the King of Ragers and to themselves as Ragers and right now, it appears their camp is fully incensed with rage. Following the tragic events at this year’s Astroworld music Festival that turned fatal, the host and convener of the concert, Travis Scott is now facing numerous lawsuits. Over a 100 lawsuits have now been filed against him with the number alarmingly increasing daily. 
The Festival which was held in Houston left 10 dead and hundreds of other attendees injured and hospitalized. Travis and the organizers of the event are now facing a massive lawsuit filed against them by more than 125 of his fans who attended the concert, including the family of one of the victims who died at the festival.
